InStat makes your training process and performance tech-savvy. We tag every action on the court, link it to the video of the episode and visualize on our video-platform.
InStat Scout is a unique tool for coaches, athletes, scouts, video-analysts, agents, managers and other sport professionals. We provide them with an up-to-date customizable app, which helps to analyze the game & videos, download and share episodes via email and messengers.

InStat Scout. Basketball offers:
-          Box score and advanced statistics;
-          Full matches, ball-in-play mode, ready-made playlists;
-          Offline mode;
-          Metrics for lineups performance assessment;
-          Play type breakdown and all the pre-shooting combinations;
-          Exclusive InStat Index and various efficiency ratings;
-          Unlimited sharing opportunities.

140 000+ athletes & 49 000+ teams in InStat database.

Maximize your performance at the court with InStat tools.

Jumping rope is one of the most popular cardio exercises. Jumping rope is useful both for weight loss and for improving the functional qualities of the athlete. They are used in almost every sport: fitness, martial arts, crossfit and many others.

The rope is a very compact sports equipment that does not take up much space. You can always take it with you outside or even on vacation.

The training program for 1000 jumping rope is based on the principle of progressive growth of the exercise. And even if now you can do just a few jumps, in a couple of weeks you will be able to increase your result by an order of magnitude.

Application functions:
- levels from 0 to 1000 repetitions;
- training history
- quick statistics;
- achievements;
- reminders;

· Record your fitness accurately
Support running, cycling, walking and other activities;
· Multi-dimensional evaluation of body state
Make fitness, weight loss and exercise more scientific through FitFly;
Each exercise can obtain professional physiological indexes, so that exercise more scientific and effective;
· Find more fun in life
Support exercise track record, playback of your fitness records;
Tips:
This application supports Apple Health. With authorization, you can synchronize your steps, sleep, heart rate and other health data to Apple Health.
